# Cross-origin isolation + privacy CSP (architecture spec §7.1, §11).
#
# This file is understood natively by Netlify and Cloudflare Pages. For other
# static hosts, configure the equivalent response headers (see README §Deployment).
#
# COOP/COEP are REQUIRED for SharedArrayBuffer (the audio ring buffer) — the most
# common deployment gotcha (spec §11). The CSP's `connect-src 'self'` makes it
# structurally impossible for the page to exfiltrate audio or transcripts.

# Default `connect-src` allows ONLY the Hugging Face model origin (first-load
# weight download). For STRICT/air-gapped mode, self-host weights and reduce
# `connect-src` to `'self'` (drop the huggingface.co/hf.co entries).

/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: same-origin
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'wasm-unsafe-eval'; worker-src 'self' blob:; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data:; font-src 'self'; connect-src 'self' https://huggingface.co https://*.huggingface.co https://*.hf.co; object-src 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'none'; frame-ancestors 'none'
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: no-referrer
